=== Async Exception Handling Test ===

Test 1: Basic try-catch
Executing successful operation
Success: success (code 200)

Test 2: Catching async exception
Executing failing operation
Caught exception: Async operation failed

Test 3: Finally block
Executing successful operation
Operation completed: success
Finally block executed

Test 4: Exception propagation
Outer call awaiting inner
Inner call throwing exception
Caught propagated exception: Inner failure

Test 5: Multiple catch blocks
Caught RuntimeException: Runtime error in async
Cleanup in finally

All async exception handling tests complete
